</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Subaru 最新 Forester e-BOXER 到港，擁智能安全輔助系統</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/26/forester-e-boxer/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=forester-e-boxer</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 26 Nov 2021 11:58:38 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1073215</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>香港 Subaru 代理意美汽車宣布，全新 2022 Forester e-BOXER 正式登陸香港。 &#038;nbsp [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>香港 Subaru 代理意美汽車宣布，全新 2022 Forester e-BOXER 正式登陸香港。</p><p>第 5 代小改款的 Forester e-BOXER 以全新的「Bolder」設計理念，帶來猶如鷹眼般銳利的 LED 頭，Subaru 家族六角型鬼面罩及雙色削切 18 吋鋁合金輪圈，增添充滿野性及更強烈的運動風格。除了延續以往具代表性的經典顏色，亦加入了 3 款大地系列車色，包括 Brilliant Bronze Metallic，Autumn Green Metallic 及 Cascade Green Silica，令 Forester 愛好者有更豐富的選擇。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-25.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073230" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-25-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-25-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-25-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-25.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-15.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-15-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-15-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-15-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-15.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073223" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-6-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>新一代 e-BOXER 不僅承傳了 Subaru 的 Subaru Global Platform SGP 全球模組化底盤、Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive SAWD 左右平衡全時間四輪驅、Boxer Engine 水平對向引擎及 EyeSight 4.0 智能駕駛安全輔助系統這 4 大核心科技外，更進行了多項改革改進。</p><p>在 EyeSight 4.0 基礎上新增「線道維持置中功能 Lane Centering Function」，此有助車輛於垂直線維持置中外，於微彎線道更能發揮作用，讓操作更細膩。另外，亦加入了「線道防偏功能 Lane Departure Prevention」功能的「線道防偏離警示 Lane Departure Warning」，當系統偵測駕駛者以 60km/h 或以上行駛，但未有使用指揮燈的情況下，又即將偏離原有線道時，系統會幫助駕駛者自動校正並重回線道內。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0020-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073227" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0020-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0020-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0020-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0020-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Subaru 更升級了可調式 X-MODE 越野系統，當車速超過 40km/h 時自動轉回「Stand by」模式，如低過 35km/h 時會自動轉至「X-MODE」模式，讓駕駛者更易操控，更能專注面對濕滑的路面。再者，X-MODE 中的「斜坡緩降功能 Hill Descent Control」亦更人性化，當駕駛者想從功能運作時加速，煞車的自動調節、油門輸入與制動系統之間更順暢，駕駛者更能輕鬆駕馭香港陡峭的山路及多層停車場。</p><p>本於 Subaru 的 SI-DRIVE 設有 Sport（S）及 Intelligent（I）2 項駕駛模式，而全新敏銳反應的 SI-DRIVE e-Active Shift Control 功能更獨有配備在新一代 e-BOXER 中，該功能會於 SI-DRIVE 的 Sport（S）出現。系統會於駕駛者在彎前煞車時，自動降下波檔，令引擎轉數提升及於出彎時有更敏銳的加速表現；Intelligent（I）模式則繼續以環保慳油為重。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0021-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0021-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0021-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0021-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0021-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0025-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073231" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0025-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0025-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0025-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0025-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>全新 Forester e-BOXER 現己接受訂購，售價為港幣＄349,800，買家可於專頁或親臨 Subaru 九龍灣旗艦店參觀。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0029-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073232" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0029-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0029-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0029-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0029-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>規格</p><p>排氣量：1995cc</p><p>引擎最大馬力：150PS</p><p>最大扭力：196Nm</p><p>電動馬達最大馬力：16.7PS</p><p>電動馬達最大扭力：66Nm</p><p>傳動系統：左右平衡式全時間四輪推動、主動扭力分配系統</p><p>車價：$349,800</p><p>資料來源：SUBARU</p><p>—</p><div class="css-16zmdoi" data-is-focusable="true">unwire.hk Mewe 專頁：<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></div></p><div class="feedflare">
